<section class="cp-how">
  <div class="cp-how__inner">
    <p class="cp-how__eyebrow">How it works</p>
    <h2 class="cp-how__heading">From setup to scoreboard in 3 steps.</h2>
    <div class="cp-how__steps">
      <div class="cp-step">
        <div class="cp-step__bar"></div>
        <div class="cp-step__num">01</div>
        <h3 class="cp-step__title">Build your event</h3>
        <p class="cp-step__body">Add players, pick a format (Americano, Mexicano, League), set your courts and rounds. <span style="text-transform:none">cørt</span> Play generates the full draw in seconds.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cp-step">
        <div class="cp-step__bar" style="background:rgba(255,234,0,0.4);"></div>
        <div class="cp-step__num">02</div>
        <h3 class="cp-step__title">Run it live</h3>
        <p class="cp-step__body">Players scan a QR code on court to enter scores. The leaderboard updates in real time — on screen, on phone, always accurate.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cp-step">
        <div class="cp-step__bar"></div>
        <div class="cp-step__num">03</div>
        <h3 class="cp-step__title">Ratings update automatically</h3>
        <p class="cp-step__body">When the event closes, every player's <span style="text-transform:none">cørt</span> Rating updates based on their results. No admin. No spreadsheets. Done.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

